  autocmd!
  autocmd CmdlineEnter,CmdwinLeave : call s:cmdl_enter()
  autocmd CmdlineLeave,CmdwinEnter : call s:cmdl_leave()
  autocmd CmdlineLeave : call s:clean()
augroup END

